This folder contain the Hamming code and Hamming Matrix

HAMMING MATRIX

generate a matrix for a hamming code, the size must be define in the source.

hamming_matrix.c

make matrix

HAMMIN CODE
encode and decode according to the rate define (m,n)

bit_counter  
bit_operation
bit_operation
define
hamming

make 




